author: LMD
long_description:
Cellestiall (**cell**-esti-**all**) extends Cellestial to the entire world. Accordingly depends on [`cellestial`](https://github.com/appgurueu/cellestial).

Part of the Cellestial Series: [`cellestial`](https://content.luanti.org/packages/LMD/cellestial/), `cellestiall` and [`cellestial_game`](https://content.luanti.org/packages/LMD/cellestial_game/)
name: cellestiall
short_description: Simulates 3D cellular automata in your entire world. WARNING: you will lose items & buildings in your world.
title: World of Life
